_sText:
Map by Rouge6 - This fun aim map contains explosive barrels in the middle of the map that explode and cause cannisters and furniture to fly across the map. This map WILL improve your headshot percentage, GUARENTEED. - this map has been tested in beta 3 different times, and has been tested amongst several players and they have expressed approval that this map can now be released. enjoy! 

reguards, Rouge6. supports 16 players/ server approved!
